prodNameC: 鼻咽定康 EB 病毒蛋白衣抗原 IgM 抗體檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Microelisa strip plate：Holder with 96 wells each coated with monoclonal anti-human IgM (mouse)
Conjugate：Monoclonal anti-VCA p18 (rat) conjugated with horseradish peroxiase.
Conjugate diluent：Synthetic VCA peptide in MES buffer (lyophilized).
Reconstitution solution：Deionized water.
Calibrator I：Human serum containing 5 AU anti-VCA p 18 IgM/ml (nonreactive level).
Calibrator II：Human serum containing 20 AU anti-VCA p 18 IgM/ml (cut-off level).
Calibrator III：Human serum containing 80 AU anti-VCA p 18 IgM/ml (reactive level).
Calibrator IV：Human serum containing 140 AU anti-VCA p 18 IgM/ml (high reactive level).
Sample Diluent：Phosphate buffer. Preservative：Pro Clin 300 (0.2%).
Phosphate buffer concentrate：Concentrated (25x) phosphate buffer with 0.05% tween-20.
TMB substrate：Tetramethylbenzidine and peroxide in citrate buffer.
Stop Solution：0.2 mol/l sulfuric acid.
applicantName: 香港商生物梅里埃有限公司台灣分公司
applicantAddr: 台北市松山區南京東路5段34號4樓
efficacy: 以酵素免疫分析法測定人體血清或血漿中 EBV VCA IgM Ab.
